title: 5900+ Cocktail Recipes
description: 5900+ Cocktail Recipes contains over 5900 cocktail recipes for professional bartenders or the home bartender.  Included are standard and the newer, more hip cocktails.  An index is included to aid in finding cocktails faster, without having to flip through 750+ pages of recipes.  The end of the book contains blank pages allowing you to write your own recipes for safe keeping.  This is a preview copy of the printed version of 5900+ Cocktail Recipes containing 136 recipes.
